project: Welcome, casual, to the tutorial. I'm here to school you on how to play vidja gaymes. You are playing as Bob, the little purple square dude. If you have a Co-op buddy, then he's playing as Dave, the cyan square.
Bottom Text Venezuela Iphone CXV 1 Billion Dead Vine "Boom" Sound

You can use the A & D keys to make Bob walk left and right, and the arrow keys to do the same with Dave. Though if you didn't know how the WASD keys worked, I'd question how you're still breathing without a brain.
Press the W key or the up arrow in order to jump. Again, baby stuff. You know all of this already. Let's move on.
You can use springs such as this in order to reach greater heights.
You can fall through black platforms such as this by pressing S or Down arrow. Easy stuff.

^ This is a Power Up. There'll be more kinds once this game is more finished, but as of right now the Grow Arrow is the only one. It makes you much bigger and much more dense for 15 seconds, letting you hit the ball harder and move physics objects easier. Use it to destroy that wall.
Watch out for pits. If you fall in one, Dr. War Crimes arrives at the Balkans. Also you have to restart the level.
This is the ball. The objective of every level is to get it into the goal, which will return you to the level-select stage.
This is the goal. Get the ball into it to complete the level and return to the level select stage.
